  "short_description": "Exitium is a horror story game that lasts 3-4 hours. Right after being broken up with, you died. You open your eyes in a creepy black and white place, chased by monsters. You have to find out what happened to you by finding pieces of your memory and choosing between forgiveness or revenge.",
