  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY</h2> He wants to talk, she meets him at their favorite spot, by the frozen lake.<br>He doesn't want to be with her anymore. Before any explanation, the ice breaks and she's now slowly drowning in cold and dark water.<br><strong>Trapped between two realities</strong>, trying to <strong>escape</strong> her own demons, gathering pieces of her life with him, she will have to <strong>choose between forgiveness and revenge</strong>.<br><br>A <i>very unsettling story</i> in a game where nothing is what it appears to be.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>2 different game mecanics<br></li><li>Mind twisting story<br></li><li>Puzzles<br></li><li>Original graphical universe<br></li><li>Universe based ambient/electro music</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1180450/extras/9d4a0ad4b2d86f9a4f6c6d44f7ea1bb0.poster.avif?t=1592586781\" width=466 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1180450/extras/9d4a0ad4b2d86f9a4f6c6d44f7ea1bb0.webm?t=1592586781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1180450/extras/9d4a0ad4b2d86f9a4f6c6d44f7ea1bb0.mp4?t=1592586781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
